# Pixel Notes Notes

## Daily Commands
- `flutter devices`
- `flutter run -d emulator-5554`
- `cd frontend && flutter analyze`
- `cd backend && PYTHONPATH=. /home/gustradev/www/pixelnotes/.venv/bin/python -m pytest ../tests/backend -q`

## Deploy Commands
- `./scripts/deploy.sh dev`
- `./scripts/deploy.sh staging`
- `./scripts/deploy.sh prod`

## Tunnel API (Named Cloudflare)
- API publik: `https://api94837.pixelsolusindo.space`
- Health check: `curl https://api94837.pixelsolusindo.space/health`
- Tunnel config file: `infra/cloudflared.pixelnotes-api.docker.yml`
- Jalankan tunnel:
  - `docker rm -f pixelnotes-api-tunnel >/dev/null 2>&1 || true`
  - `docker run -d --name pixelnotes-api-tunnel --user 0 --network host -v /home/gustradev/www/pixelnotes/infra/cloudflared.pixelnotes-api.docker.yml:/etc/cloudflared/config.yml:ro -v /home/gustradev/.cloudflared:/home/nonroot/.cloudflared:ro cloudflare/cloudflared:latest tunnel --no-autoupdate --config /etc/cloudflared/config.yml run`

## Monitoring
- `docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f infra/docker-compose.monitoring.yml up -d`

## Reminder
- Rotate all secrets in `credential.env` sebelum produksi publik.

## Secret User Credentials
- Password simbol (entry gate): `pixelentry2026`
- `SECRET_USER_1=user_alpha`
- `SECRET_USER_2=user_beta`
- Login test:
  - `user_alpha` -> `<set_local_password>`
  - `user_beta` -> `<set_local_password>`
- Password plaintext tidak tersimpan di repo (yang disimpan adalah bcrypt hash di `SECRET_PASS_1` dan `SECRET_PASS_2`).

## Set Password User (Generate Hash)
- `python scripts/enroll_user.py --username user_alpha --password "<password_baru>"`
- `python scripts/enroll_user.py --username user_beta --password "<password_baru>"`
- Copy nilai `HASH=` hasil command ke:
  - `SECRET_PASS_1` (untuk `user_alpha`)
  - `SECRET_PASS_2` (untuk `user_beta`)
